{"type":"article_comment","id":421519,"parentType":"article","parentId":20615,"uid":43123,"contents":"@我奶你一口<br>\n<br>\n我們的房產證(在臺灣叫\"房屋所有權狀\")是含公設占比的，所以你買房是是要付公設的錢的。<br>\n然後每年抽稅時也會把你分到的建築公設面積算進去，一樣按實際使用房屋面積去課1.2%的房屋稅。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n在臺灣買房都會拿到「房屋所有權狀」跟「土地所有權狀」兩個證件。<br>\n房屋每年要按面積課房屋稅，土地每年要按申報價值課地價稅，所以買房難，養房更艱難(眼眶泛淚<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CaLg99o.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CaLg99o.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/CaLg99o.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RhOv6gS.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RhOv6gS.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RhOv6gS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-23","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}